      },
      "date": "2021-01-31 20:48:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI was wondering then this would show up. I remember the ARM work which introduced this fix size of LNET_MAX_IOV. I discussed the idea of support more sizes but the argument was that o2iblnd doesn't handle larger sizes so well. Sadly this limitation was imposed on everyone.\nThis should really be an interface setting.",
